data-triple-N3.o: "Halifax County is a county located in the U.S. state of North Carolina. As of 2000, the population was 57,370. Its county seat is Halifax. Halifax County is part of the Roanoke Rapids, North Carolina, Micropolitan Statistical Area."@en
